{"tid":2016044,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】石田桃香踩過界做YouTuber　雞手鴨腳煮料理勁可愛","createTime":"2020-05-14T06:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T06:15:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7312b3ff2fd84aff906c77fdd0db64ed3ec13c1d","tid":2016044,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"22歲日本寫真偶像石田桃香因貌似上位女星有村架純，所以有「水着界有村架純」之稱，深受寫真愛好者歡迎。最近，她為雜誌到知名景點鳥取砂丘拍攝電子寫真集，當中不乏少布性感靚相，令人目不暇給。另外，她近日亦踩過界開設YouTube頻道，挑戰做YouTuber，除了寫真拍攝花絮，更有「露兩手」煮咖哩飯、煮早餐的短片，雖然雞手鴨腳，但仍然獲得不少粉絲大讚可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4484930/org/e13376604add01c8111dc9836b9e5416.jpg/T6UKKtzGJAPENwFXfre3Onpyu16fpVj4RkIAUkZCAFI?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4484930%2Forg%2Fe13376604add01c8111dc9836b9e5416.jpg%2FT6UKKtzGJAPENwFXfre3Onpyu16fpVj4RkIAUkZCAFI%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=44172434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"813aa5a47340afef5bbc7cc045434399249144a8","tid":2016044,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4484858/org/892f0f503dd44b4eaa5dc83aa69ccc35.jpg/NYrUI9gzziG3ERG1ph6uiEQTyQVwsM0eapYxe2qWMXs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4484858%2Forg%2F892f0f503dd44b4eaa5dc83aa69ccc35.jpg%2FNYrUI9gzziG3ERG1ph6uiEQTyQVwsM0eapYxe2qWMXs&h=6fb56ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4484861/org/05f22378a02d85261167ca67373c04bc.jpg/1jhVTYhpleqoC6tOgI9dvoiKtZc6dCgPlmXFgpZlxYI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4484861%2Forg%2F05f22378a02d85261167ca67373c04bc.jpg%2F1jhVTYhpleqoC6tOgI9dvoiKtZc6dCgPlmXFgpZlxYI&h=7de074e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c62f55f99ef148b2ee3f9e8641b5347067e6765","tid":2016044,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl